properties.name: type
properties.description: 类型：1->主图，2->商品详情图，3->商品标签图，4->视频，5->其它

properties.name: sort
properties.description: 排序字段(user_num:累计搜索用户数; search_num:累计搜索次数; today_search_num:今日搜索次数; yesterday_search_num:昨日搜索次数; last_week_search_num:最近一周搜索次数;  last_week_month_num:最近一月搜索次数)

properties.name: availability
properties.description: 是否在售，1 in stock, 0 out of stock, other value ignore

properties.name: coupon
properties.description: 是否支持coupon, 用于discover, 0, 1, 非必选项

properties.name: sortBy
properties.description: 排序字段，可选值: default(默认算法排序), sale(销量), retailPrice(价格), _score(评分), review(评价), publishTime(发布时间)

properties.name: sortOrder
properties.description: 排序方向，默认DESC，接受ASC, DESC
